{"word":"Simeon","slug":"simeon","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Simeon</b> <a href=\"#/H8095\">H8095</a> <br/> 1. Son of Jacob:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=33'>Gen 29:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=23'>Gen 35:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=1&verse=2'>Exo 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=1'>1Ch 2:1</a> <br/> - With Levi avenges upon the Shemchemites the seduction of Dinah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=34'>Gen 34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=7'>Gen 49:7</a> <br/> - Jacob's denunciation of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=34&verse=30'>Gen 34:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=7'>Gen 49:7</a> <br/> - Goes down into Egypt to buy corn; is bound by Joseph and detained<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=24'>Gen 42:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=36'>Gen 42:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=23'>Gen 43:23</a> <br/> - His sons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=46&verse=10'>Gen 46:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=15'>Exo 6:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=37'>1Ch 4:37</a> <br/> - Descendants of<br/> b General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=14'>Num 26:14</a><br/> 2. Tribe of:<br/> - Military enrollment of:<br/> b at Sinai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=23'>Num 1:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=13'>Num 2:13</a><br/> b in the plains of Moab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=14'>Num 26:14</a><br/> - Place of, in camp and march<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=12'>Num 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=19'>Num 10:19</a> <br/> - Inheritance allotted to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=9'>Jos 19:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=17'>Jdg 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=43'>1Ch 4:43</a> <br/> - Stood on Mount Gerizim to bless at the time of the rehearsal of the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=12'>Deu 27:12</a> <br/> - Joined with the people of Judah and Benjamin in the renewal of the Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=15&verse=15'>2Ch 15:15</a> <br/> - Idolatry of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=34&verse=7'>2Ch 34:7</a><br/><a href='S:Israel'>Israel</a> <br/> 3. A devout man in Jerusalem, blesses Jesus in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=35'>Luk 2:35</a><br/> 4. An ancestor of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=30'>Luk 3:30</a><br/> 5. A disciple, called also Niger<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=1'>Act 13:1</a><br/> 6. Name given to Peter<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=14'>Act 15:14</a><br/><a href='S:Peter'>Peter</a> "}]}